I then ran with bazel-bin/tensorflow/tensorboard/tensorboard --logdir /home/ubuntu and the Graph tab is still giving me the Uncaught TypeError: Polymer.dom(...).unobserveNodes is not a function error and showing a blank page other than the header bar (title and tab links). Any suggestions?
